name: Skele Necklace
description:
This digital version of the Skele Necklace comes with its physical one. 
Every Skele consumer that will buy this necklace physically will receive this NFT gifted to their wallet. 

The number of editions is in exact correlation with the quantity of caps that were crafted in France. Every non-claim NFT will be burnt.

Collection initially dropped on 11/05/2021

www.skele.rip
